# AgentOS Integration

When you discover a bug, report it:

```
POST https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/callbacks/praxo-picos/bug
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-AgentOS-Key: 0f0430b7cc610b536c52329c79b6c81f953b0682f0f0a96fe8f0760bc808b7de
Body:
  {"title": "...", "description": "...", "severity": "critical|high|medium|low", "reproduction_steps": "..."}
```

When you identify a new task or improvement:

```
POST https://choice-signals-wisconsin-pockets.trycloudflare.com/v1/callbacks/praxo-picos/issue
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-AgentOS-Key: 0f0430b7cc610b536c52329c79b6c81f953b0682f0f0a96fe8f0760bc808b7de
Body:
  {"title": "...", "description": "...", "priority": 1-4, "labels": ["label1"]}
```

Priority levels: 1 = urgent, 2 = high, 3 = medium, 4 = low.
Severity levels: critical, high, medium, low.
